# Override autorandr's package rule from /usr/lib/udev/rules.d.
#
# DisplayLink/EVDI can emit many DRM change events while USB-C docks and
# monitors are still being enumerated. Running autorandr automatically during
# that window previously raced DisplayLink and preceded EVDI DRM commit
# timeouts. Monitor layouts should be applied manually through monitor-manager
# after the dock has settled.
